CLINICAL NOTICE — NOT A MEDICAL DEVICE
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

This Software is decision-support code for licensed physicians and
dietitians. It is NOT a medical device. It has NOT been reviewed or
approved by any regulatory authority (including the FDA, EMA, CDSCO, or
any national equivalent). It is NOT a substitute for independent clinical
judgement, current prescribing information, or applicable standard of
care.

Every generated plan — including GLP-1 / GIP receptor-agonist dose
schedules, intermittent-fasting windows, calorie and macronutrient
targets, and condition-specific rule outputs — MUST be reviewed by a
qualified treating clinician before any part of it is applied to a
patient. Drug dosing must be re-verified against the current prescribing
information for the patient's jurisdiction and the patient's individual
contraindications.

